PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Public Works and Government Services of CYNTHIA ENE of Cambridge Bay, Nunavut, to be a director of the board of directors of Defence Construction (1951) Limited, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of John Boyd, whose term has expired.
